        <para id="id22359880">Which one of you would like to present todayâ€™s weather to the class as it is presented on television?</para>
        <para id="id22359888">Try to get hold of a newspaper that has a weather chart each day. Cut it out and study the key that indicates the different types of weather carefully. </para>
